â€‹To prevent the Firefox "AI Control Center" from sandboxing the plugin or causing "Wakey wakey" nag errors, follow these developer steps:
â€‹1. Configure the Browser
â€‹Type about:config in your address bar.
â€‹Set xpinstall.signatures.required to false.
â€‹Set browser.ai.controlcenter.enabled to false (to disable the AI nag engine).
